OL,3,C'I actually heard the blast': 40th
OL,4,Canniversary of IRA Brighton bomb
OL,6,FEx-ITN reporter Paul Davies, one of
OL,7,Fthe first journalists on the scene,
OL,8,Freflects on the 1984 IRA attempt to
OL,9,Fkill Margaret Thatcher and how it
OL,10,Fchanged politics.
OL,12,FBy Paul Davies, Former ITV News
OL,13,FCorrespondent
OL,15,FIt was a day that would forever change
OL,16,Fthe way party conferences are held and
OL,17,Fthe security around them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
