OL,3,C'I actually heard the blast': 40th
OL,4,Canniversary of IRA Brighton bomb
OL,6,FWe didn't know that however, as we
OL,7,Fjoined politicians and their
OL,8,Fsupporters enjoying one of the social
OL,9,Fhighlights of the political calendar.
OL,11,FThe Thursday night of a Tory party
OL,12,Fconference, with all the business done
OL,13,Fand just the leader's speech to come
OL,14,Fin the morning, was traditionally a
OL,15,Ftime to let your hair down.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
