OL,3,C'I actually heard the blast': 40th
OL,4,Canniversary of IRA Brighton bomb
OL,6,FI actually heard the blast and walked
OL,7,Fout onto the seafront to see their
OL,8,Fhotel under a cloud of dust and
OL,9,Ffalling masonry.
OL,11,FPersuading colleagues still in the bar
OL,12,Fthat I had witnessed an attempt to
OL,13,Fassassinate Margaret Thatcher was the
OL,14,Ffirst challenge, but I was fortunate
OL,15,Fthat the group included a cameraman,
OL,16,Fsound recordist and lighting man.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
