OL,3,C'I actually heard the blast': 40th
OL,4,Canniversary of IRA Brighton bomb
OL,6,FWe were then able to enter the
OL,7,Fdevastated building, ITV News
OL,8,Fcameraman Nigel Thomson joining the
OL,9,Ffirst fire crews as they climbed up
OL,10,Fthrough the hotel floors searching for
OL,11,Fvictims and survivors.
OL,13,FThe images he captured that morning of
OL,14,Fthe devastation caused by the bomb and
OL,15,Fthe rescue of people who had been
OL,16,Fburied beneath the collapsed floors
OL,17,Fmust rate as some of the most
OL,18,Fremarkable footage filmed in Britain
OL,19,Fsince the Second World War.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
