OL,3,C'I actually heard the blast': 40th
OL,4,Canniversary of IRA Brighton bomb
OL,6,FMargaret Thatcher was applying
OL,7,Ffinishing touches to her end of
OL,8,Fconference speech when the explosion
OL,9,Fhappened. If she had been in the
OL,10,Fbathroom of her suite she may have
OL,11,Fbeen killed.
OL,13,FInstead she appeared in the early
OL,14,Fhours defiantly telling us the
OL,15,Fconference would go on, despite the
OL,16,Floss of five lives with many more
OL,17,Finjured.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
