OL,3,C'I actually heard the blast': 40th
OL,4,Canniversary of IRA Brighton bomb
OL,6,FIn those dramatic and confused hours
OL,7,Fwe were told that all members of the
OL,8,Fcabinet had been accounted for and
OL,9,Fwere safe. That turned out not to be
OL,10,Ftrue.
OL,12,FNorman Tebbit and his wife were later
OL,13,Ffound buried but alive. They survived
OL,14,Fbut Margaret Tebbit was paralysed from
OL,15,Fthe neck down.
