OL,3,C'I actually heard the blast': 40th
OL,4,Canniversary of IRA Brighton bomb
OL,6,FSubsequent investigations would
OL,7,Fdiscover that IRA bomber Patrick Magee
OL,8,Fhad checked into the Grand Hotel three
OL,9,Fand a half weeks earlier and left a
OL,10,Fbomb with a delay timer beneath the
OL,11,Fbath in a sixth floor room. Conference
OL,12,Fsecurity had been superficial.
OL,14,FThat would never happen again, since
OL,15,F1984 the place where a party leader,
OL,16,Fespecially a Prime Minister, stays and
OL,17,Fworks during conference will be a
OL,18,Ffortress bristling with armed police
OL,19,Fand security.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
