OL,3,C'I actually heard the blast': 40th
OL,4,Canniversary of IRA Brighton bomb
OL,6,FThe Brighton bombing ended what many
OL,7,Fsee as a time of naivety and innocence.
OL,9,FYou can watch a special programme on
OL,10,Fthe Brighton Bombing - 'Bombing
OL,11,FThatcher: Brighton's night of terror'
OL,12,F- on ITVX from 4pm Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
